text: KYES may refer to: * KYES (AM), a radio station (1180 AM) licensed to serve Rockville, Minnesota, United States * KYES-TV, a television station (channel 7, virtual 5) licensed to serve Anchorage, Alaska, United States * KYEX-LD, a low-power television station (channel 26) licensed to serve Juneau, Alaska, formerly KYES-LD (July-September 2020)
title: KYES
